#, no-wrap
msgid "Currently, the most accessible way to download big archives is to use the program FileZilla as explained in [this page](/admin/tutorials/filezilla).\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/40.backups/index.mdx:85
#, no-wrap
msgid "By default, backups are stored in `/home/yunohost.backup/archives/`.\n"
msgstr ""

